       Hell Beast remained on the bridge. He felt it was important that he 
stay, as long as Unicron needed him anyways. Otherwise he would be with his 
troops. 
       His troops, all of them, were in there section of the base. Most 
likely practicing or putting all the information they had gathered together. 
Tarantulas found the cloning technology and process very fascinating. He 
wanted to work on the project.


--part1_104.122efac.27f8e485_boundary
